Version 1.2
------------
- You can insert width and height of the thumb, 
  the class autodetect longer side of the image and create a thumb using width or height inserted

- New splitFilePath method to extract file name and path from a complete path2file string, returned from putFile
  and miniatura method (see readme for more information).
  
- minor bugs fixed (see bugs).

- thanks to Mikhael Korneev for the patch, Bob Abbott, Simon Mann, Luke Hartman for the suggestions and help.


